y of PFREY6BD or PREFY7BD1 should contact them at customerserviceteam@warnermusic.com and they will arrange a replacement disc.\n\nWe apologize for the inconvenience and stress that this may have caused to box purchasers, although we have ascertained that this unavoidable damage could not have been predicted.”\n\nThe printed duration of tracks DVD4-11 and BR4-11 \"Alan’s Psychedelic Breakfast\" (quad mix)  is 13:01. However on DVD and BD the actual track durations are only 11:58 / 11:59. The last minute of the tracks has been cut out for some reason.","released_formatted":"11 Nov 2016","identifiers":[{"type":"Barcode","value":"0190295950255"},{"type":"Matrix / Runout","value":"0190295950255 PFREY1CD1 AG42930-01 manufactured by optimal media GmbH","description":"CD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mastering SID Code","value":"IFPI L575","description":"CD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mould SID Code","value":"IFPI 9744","description":"CD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Matrix / Runout","value":"0190295950255 PFREY1CD2 AG42933-01 manufactured by optimal media GmbH","description":"CD2 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mastering SID Code","value":"IFPI L575","description":"CD2 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mould SID Code","value":"IFPI 9746","description":"CD2 1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Matrix / Runout","value":"0190295950255 PFREY1DVD V3 DG45264-01 manufactured by optimal media GmbH","description":"DVD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mastering SID Code","value":"IFPI L575","description":"DVD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mould SID Code","value":"IFPI 9747","description":"DVD1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Matrix / Runout","value":"EG42978-01 0190295950255 PFREY1BD optimal media GmbH","description":"BR1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mastering SID Code","value":"IFPI LZ08","description":"BR1 (1965-1967 Cambridge St/ation)"},{"type":"Mould SID Code","value":"